Package filesprocessing.filefilters

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AllFileFilter
    Filters all the given files
    BetweenFileFilter
    Filters files two given file size value
    ContainsFileFilter
    Filters files that contain a string in the name
    ExecutableFileFilter
    Filter files that can be executed, or non-executable, depending on the state the filter is initialized with
    FileFilterFactory
    File filter factory class
    FileNameFileFilter
    Filters files according to file name
    GreaterThanFileFilter
    Filters files greater than a given file size value
    HiddenFileFilter
    Filter files that are hidden/not-hidden, depending on the state the filter initialized with
    PrefixFileFilter
    Filters files that their name start with a given prefix
    SmallerThanFileFilter
    Filters files smaller than a given value.
    SuffixFileFilter
    Filters files that their name end with a given suffix
    WritableFileFilter
    Writable file filter
